header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-gear")
                span System
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 시스템 설정
        button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
            span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 xl:grid-cols-[460px_1fr]")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") General
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목, favicon, 사이드바 로고를 저장 시 한 번에 적용합니다.
                div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 브라우저 제목
                        input(type="text", data-testid="system-browser-title", [(ngModel)]="general.browser_title", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Favicon
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SVG, PNG, ICO를 지원합니다.
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img([src]="previewUrl('favicon')", alt="favicon", class="h-8 w-8 rounded object-contain")
                            input(id="system-favicon-upload", type="file", accept=".ico,.png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('favicon', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-favicon-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('favicon')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('favicon')") {{pendingAssetName('favicon')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('favicon')") Favicon 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                            div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                div
                                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Sidebar Logo
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 좌측 메뉴 상단에 표시되는 브랜드 이미지
                                div(class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950")
                                    img(*ngIf="previewUrl('logo')", [src]="previewUrl('logo')", alt="logo", class="h-full w-full object-contain")
                                    span(*ngIf="!previewUrl('logo')", class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-400") 없음
                            input(id="system-logo-upload", type="file", accept=".png,.svg,.gif,.jpg,.jpeg,.webp", class="hidden", (change)="selectAsset('logo', $event)")
                            div(class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                button(type="button", (click)="openAssetPicker('system-logo-upload')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-image")
                                    span 이미지 선택
                                button(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')", type="button", (click)="clearSelectedAsset('logo')", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                    i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
                                    span 선택 취소
                            p(class="mt-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                                span(*ngIf="hasPendingAsset('logo')") {{pendingAssetName('logo')}} 파일을 선택했습니다. 저장 시 업로드됩니다.
                                span(*ngIf="!hasPendingAsset('logo')") Logo 경로는 고정되어 있으며 새 이미지를 저장하면 기존 파일을 대체합니다.

                    button(type="button", data-testid="system-general-save", (click)="saveGeneral()", [disabled]="savingGeneral()", class="inline-flex h-10 w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                        span {{savingGeneral() ? '저장 중...' : '일반 설정 저장'}}

            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 xl:grid-cols-2")
                div(*ngFor="let integration of integrations", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                    div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div
                            h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{integration.label}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{integration.enabled ? '연결 정보를 저장하고 연결 테스트를 수행할 수 있습니다.' : '현재 사용 안 함 상태입니다.'}}
                        label(class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300")
                            input(type="checkbox", [attr.data-testid]="'integration-' + integration.key + '-enabled'", [(ngModel)]="integration.enabled")
                            span 사용
                    div(class="space-y-4 p-4")
                        div(*ngIf="integration.enabled", class="space-y-4")
                            label(*ngFor="let field of integration.field_entries", class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{field.label}}
                                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="integration.fields[field.key]", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")

                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{integration.secret_name}}
                                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                    input([type]="secretInputType(integration)", [attr.data-testid]="'integration-' + integration.key + '-secret'", [(ngModel)]="integration.secret_value", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="toggleSecret(integration)", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="integration.secret_visible ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
                        div(*ngIf="!integration.enabled", class="rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 px-3 py-4 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            | 사용을 켜면 URL, 계정, 비밀번호 또는 token 입력란이 표시됩니다.

                        div(class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:flex-row")
                            button(*ngIf="integration.enabled", type="button", (click)="testIntegration(integration)", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-sky-300 bg-sky-50 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-800 hover:bg-sky-100 dark:border-sky-900/70 dark:bg-sky-950/30 dark:text-sky-200 dark:hover:bg-sky-950/50")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-plug-circle-check")
                                span 연결 테스트
                            button(type="button", [attr.data-testid]="'integration-save-' + integration.key", (click)="saveIntegration(integration)", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                                span 설정 저장

        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                div
                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 웹서버 및 SSL
                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 중인 웹서버의 설정 파일 위치와 SSL 인증서 파일 경로를 관리합니다.
                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(webserver()?.active_server === 'none' ? 'missing' : 'active')")
                        | {{activeServerLabel()}}
                    button(type="button", (click)="saveWebserver()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                        span 웹서버 설정 저장
            div(class="space-y-5 p-4")
                div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4")
                    div(*ngFor="let server of visibleServerEntries()", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 p-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                            div
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{server.label}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{server.version || '설치 정보를 확인하지 못했습니다.'}}
                            span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(server.daemon_status)")
                                | {{serverStatusLabel(server)}}
                        div(class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-2")
                            div
                                p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 바이너리 경로
                                p(class="mt-1 break-all text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{server.binary_path || '-'}}
                            div
                                p(class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 데몬 이름
                                p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{server.service_name || '-'}}
                        div(*ngIf="server.installed", class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2")
                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 메인 설정 파일 경로
                                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="server.settings.config_path", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openServerPathPicker(server.key, 'config_path', 'file')", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-folder-open")
                                p(class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 감지값: {{server.detected_paths?.config_path || '-'}}
                            label(class="block")
                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 사이트 설정 디렉토리
                                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="server.settings.site_path", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openServerPathPicker(server.key, 'site_path', 'directory')", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-folder-tree")
                                p(class="mt-1 text-[11px] text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 감지값: {{server.detected_paths?.site_path || '-'}}
                        div(*ngIf="!server.installed", class="mt-4 rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 px-3 py-4 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400")
                            | 현재 서버에 {{server.label}} 이(가) 설치되어 있지 않습니다.

                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
                        div
                            h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") SSL 인증서 파일
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") cert 파일과 key 파일 경로를 등록하면 만료일과 SAN 정보를 즉시 분석합니다.
                        div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                            span(*ngFor="let item of certificateSummaryItems()", class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(item.tone === 'success' ? 'valid' : (item.tone === 'warning' ? 'expiring' : 'error'))")
                                | {{item.label}} {{item.value}}
                            button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                                span 인증서 추가
                    div(*ngIf="webserver()?.certificates?.length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                        | 등록된 SSL 인증서 경로가 없습니다.
                    div(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        div(*ngFor="let cert of webserver()?.certificates", class="px-4 py-4")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between")
                                div(class="min-w-0")
                                    div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                        p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{cert.label || cert.cert_path}}
                                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(cert.status)") {{cert.status}}
                                    p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") CERT {{cert.cert_path || '-'}}
                                    p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") KEY {{cert.key_path || '-'}}
                                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openCertificateModal(cert)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                    button(type="button", (click)="deleteCertificate(cert)", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-rose-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")
                            div(class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 text-xs md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4")
                                div
                                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 유효 기간
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{formatDate(cert.not_before)}} ~ {{formatDate(cert.not_after)}}
                                div
                                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 남은 기간
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{cert.days_remaining ?? '-'}}일
                                div
                                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 발급자
                                    p(class="mt-1 break-all text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{cert.issuer || '-'}}
                                div
                                    p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 키 파일
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200") {{cert.key_exists ? '존재함' : '없음'}}
                            div(*ngIf="cert.dns_names?.length > 0", class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2")
                                span(*ngFor="let name of cert.dns_names", class="inline-flex rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300") {{name}}
                            p(*ngIf="cert.message", class="mt-2 text-xs text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300") {{cert.message}}

div(*ngIf="certificateModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="w-full max-w-2xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{certificateForm.id ? 'SSL 인증서 경로 수정' : 'SSL 인증서 경로 추가'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") PEM/CRT 인증서 파일과 key 파일 경로를 입력하세요.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeCertificateModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 p-5 md:grid-cols-2")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="certificateForm.label", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 인증서 파일 경로
                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="certificateForm.cert_path", placeholder="/etc/ssl/certs/example.pem", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    button(type="button", (click)="openCertificatePathPicker('cert_path')", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-folder-open")
            label(class="block md:col-span-2")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 키 파일 경로
                div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="certificateForm.key_path", placeholder="/etc/ssl/private/example.key", class="h-10 min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 focus:border-zinc-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                    button(type="button", (click)="openCertificatePathPicker('key_path')", class="inline-flex h-10 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                        i(class="fa-solid fa-folder-open")
            label(class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 md:col-span-2")
                input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="certificateForm.enabled")
                span 이 인증서를 상태 점검에 포함
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeCertificateModal()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                span 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveCertificate()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                span 저장

div(*ngIf="pathPickerOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/50 px-4 py-6")
    div(class="flex max-h-[calc(100vh-3rem)] w-full max-w-4xl flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-2xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{pathPickerTitle()}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{pathPickerDescription()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closePathPicker()", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-600 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 p-5")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto_auto_auto_auto]")
                label(class="block lg:col-span-1")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 경로 이동
                    input(type="text", [ngModel]="pathPickerInput()", (ngModelChange)="pathPickerInput.set($event)", (keydown.enter)="jumpToPathPickerPath()", placeholder="예: /etc/nginx 또는 ~/ssl", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                button(type="button", (click)="jumpToPathPickerPath()", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right")
                    span 이동
                button(type="button", (click)="browseLocalFiles('')", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-house")
                    span 홈
                button(type="button", (click)="togglePathPickerHidden()", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="pathPickerShowHidden() ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
                    span {{pathPickerShowHidden() ? '숨김 감추기' : '숨김 보기'}}
                button(*ngIf="pathPickerMode() === 'directory' && pathPickerPath()", type="button", (click)="selectCurrentDirectory()", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-check")
                    span 현재 폴더 선택
            div(*ngIf="!pathPickerPath() && pathPickerBusy()", class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                span 파일 목록을 불러오는 중입니다.
            div(*ngIf="pathPickerPath()", class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                button(*ngFor="let crumb of pathPickerCrumbs()", type="button", (click)="browseLocalFiles(crumb.path)", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") {{crumb.label}}
                button(*ngIf="pathPickerPath() !== '/'", type="button", (click)="browsePathPickerParent()", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up")
                    span 상위 폴더
            div(class="overflow-hidden rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                div(class="max-h-[60vh] overflow-auto")
                    div(*ngIf="pathPickerBusy() && pathPickerItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 파일 목록을 불러오는 중입니다.
                    div(*ngIf="!pathPickerBusy() && pathPickerItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 파일이 없습니다.
                    div(*ngFor="let item of pathPickerItems()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-100 px-4 py-3 last:border-b-0 dark:border-zinc-800")
                        div(class="min-w-0 flex-1")
                            button(*ngIf="item.type === 'folder'", type="button", (click)="browseLocalFiles(item.path)", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 hover:text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-50 dark:hover:text-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-folder text-amber-500")
                                span(class="truncate") {{item.name}}
                            div(*ngIf="item.type !== 'folder'", class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-file-lines text-zinc-400")
                                span(class="truncate") {{item.name}}
                            p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.path}}
                        div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                            span(class="text-xs text-zinc-400 dark:text-zinc-500") {{item.type === 'folder' ? '폴더' : (item.size || 0) + ' B'}}
                            button(*ngIf="pathPickerCanSelect(item)", type="button", (click)="selectPathItem(item)", [disabled]="pathPickerBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid fa-check")
                                span {{pathPickerActionLabel(item)}}
